Bone of the father...

1283
01:55:49,800 --> 01:55:52,598
...unwillingly given.

1284
01:55:59,160 --> 01:56:02,072
Flesh of the servant...

1285
01:56:04,039 --> 01:56:07,076
...willingly sacrificed.

1286
01:56:10,999 --> 01:56:14,594
And blood of the enemy...

1287
