My wand. Wormtail.

1291
01:57:46,999 --> 01:57:48,876
Hold out your arm.

1292
01:57:49,040 --> 01:57:50,598
Master.

1293
01:57:50,760 --> 01:57:53,274
Thank you. master.

1294
01:57:53,439 --> 01:57:54,838
The other arm. Wormtail.

1295
01:58:33,800 --> 01:58:35,631
Welcome. my friends.

1296
01:58:37,000 --> 01:58:39,639
Thirteen years it's been. and yet...

1297
01:58:40,239 --> 01:58:45,518
...here you stand before me
as though it were only yesterday.

1298
01:58:46,439 --> 01:58:49,237
